premise_source_doc_sentence: Jessica Walter  (  born January 31 , 1941  )  is an American actress .

She is known for appearing in the films Play Misty for Me and Grand Prix , her role as Lucille Bluth on the sitcom Arrested Development , and providing the voice of Malory Archer in the FX animated series Archer .

Walter was a series regular for the first half of season one of 90210 , provided the voice of Fran Sinclair in the series Dinosaurs , and starred as the title character of the series Amy Prentiss , for which she won the Emmy Award for Outstanding Lead Actress in a Miniseries or TV Movie .
In addition to the original cast , Little Fockers features Jessica Alba , Laura Dern and Harvey Keitel .

Portrayed by Jessica Lowndes , the character was originally only scripted as a guest spot in the series ' pilot , but was added to the main cast in the fourteenth episode of the first season , replacing Jessica Walter .

Season one regular cast members include Rob Estes , Shenae Grimes , Tristan Wilds , Jessica Stroup , Dustin Milligan , Ryan Eggold , AnnaLynne McCord , Michael Steger , Lori Loughlin , and Jessica Walter .
His sister is actress Jessica Walter .
